  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK704">
<l>kuṟittatu kūṟāmaik koḷvārō ṭēṉai </l>
<l>yuṟuppō raṉaiyarāl vēṟu.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who understand one's thoughts without being informed (thereof) and those who do not, may (indeed) resemble one another bodily; still are they different (mentally).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
